text: Tess Olofsson (born 24 January 1988) is a Swedish international football referee. She has been an international football since 2016. ==Career== Since 2018, Olofsson has been a referee in the Swedish Svenska Cupen. Olofsson was appointed to be a referee at the UEFA Women's Euro 2022 in England. ==References== Category:Swedish sportspeople Category:Sportswomen Category:Living people Category:1988 births Category:Association football referees
